This paper discusses a sensitivity analysis study of a complex artificial intelligence system, specifically Pathfinder. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The study also involves analyzing the system's performance, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper discusses the extension of decision analytic sensitivity analysis, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
